snippet.title: CellCraft Promotional Video
snippet.description:
This video shows off the biologically-accurate real-time strategy / defense game CellCraft.  The game allows players to experience the world as a simulated cell, through the course of a wacky plot, while also learning about cellular biology.

The game was made possible by a grant from the Digital Media & Learning Competition.
